text: Dolgany () is a rural locality (a village) in Levinskoye Rural Settlement, Bolshesosnovsky District, Perm Krai, Russia. The population was 7 as of 2010. == Geography == It is located 6.5 km south-east from Levino. == References == Category:Rural localities in Bolshesosnovsky District
title: Dolgany, Perm Krai
